{"tid":1082781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[3月的結束就是4月的開始] 入嚟留低你嘅目標!","createTime":"2019-03-29T07:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T07:35:02.000Z","uid":82070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cc8c06601d9e13d6a4051f492a99838812d50772","tid":1082781,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"番番下工，突然諗番起以前讀書嘅生活，<br />\n<br />\n為咗入大學而讀書、為咗入校隊而練波、為咗追女神而學Gel頭，<br />\n<br />\n諗番起都覺得嗰陣好青春、好熱血。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到依家出到嚟做嘢，全副精神都攞哂嚟番工，放工之後個人做咩都冇哂火咁，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我決定為自己定下一個目標，然後喺4月完成佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個目標好簡單，就係重返籃球場，每個星期抽一日放工後去打波。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你情況同我一樣，想改變現狀，歡迎你喺呢個post留低你嘅目標，之後喺呢個4月一齊努力完成佢。<br />\n<br />\n如果你對自己冇信心，你都可以喺google form留低你嘅資料，當係搵個人傾下、支持下自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共勉之<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/pLbL5XxzTjm8mRS78\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FpLbL5XxzTjm8mRS78&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=4442690b\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/pLbL5XxzTjm8mRS78</a>"}]}